{"parse":{"title":"Vivo Class","pageid":31358597,"revid":855611250,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn org\">Vivo Class</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Vivo_Logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"New corporate logo of Vivo.\"><img alt=\"New corporate logo of Vivo.\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/07/Vivo_Logo.png/300px-Vivo_Logo.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"75\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/07/Vivo_Logo.png/450px-Vivo_Logo.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/07/Vivo_Logo.png/600px-Vivo_Logo.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"3092\" data-file-height=\"768\" /></a></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Types_of_business_entity\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Types of business entity\">Type of business</a></th><td class=\"category\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Privately_held_company\" title=\"Privately held company\">Private</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Available&#160;in</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/English_language\" title=\"English language\">English</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/London,_UK\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"London, UK\">London, UK</a> (2007<span style=\"display:none\">&#160;(<span class=\"bday dtstart published updated\">2007</span>)</span>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Area&#160;served</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/United_Kingdom\" title=\"United Kingdom\">United Kingdom</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/United_States\" title=\"United States\">United States</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Australia\" title=\"Australia\">Australia</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Thailand\" title=\"Thailand\">Thailand</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\nVivo Rewards Limited</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Entrepreneurship\" title=\"Entrepreneurship\">Founder(s)</a></th><td>\nGeorge Grima, Sam Rickett</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Industry</th><td class=\"category\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Education\" title=\"Education\">Education</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Product_(business)\" title=\"Product (business)\">Products</a></th><td>\nSchool Positive Behaviour platform</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Website</th><td class=\"url\">\n<span class=\"url\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vivoclass.com\">www<wbr />.vivoclass<wbr />.com</a></span></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Registration</th><td>\nRequired</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Launched</th><td>\n2007</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current&#160;status</th><td class=\"category\">\nActive</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><p><b>Vivo Class </b>(formerly <b>Vivo Miles</b>) is a <a href=\"/wiki/Privately_held_company\" title=\"Privately held company\">private company</a> based in <a href=\"/wiki/London\" title=\"London\">London</a>, UK that sells a web-based <a href=\"/wiki/Reward_(psychology)#Psychological_reward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reward (psychology)\">rewards</a> system to schools.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Founded in 2007, it was first used at <a href=\"/wiki/Westminster_Academy_(London)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Westminster Academy (London)\">Westminster Academy in London</a>.\n</p><p>In August 2014, Vivo Miles was rebranded as Vivo Class for teachers.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Rewards_in_Schools\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rewards in Schools</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Mechanism\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mechanism</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Financial_Learning\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Financial Learning</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Parental_involvement\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Parental involvement</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Financial_Value\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Financial Value</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Awards_and_nominations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Awards and nominations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Further_reading\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Further reading</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">10</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards_in_Schools\">Rewards in Schools</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards in Schools\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rewards systems are implemented in schools to praise students for positive actions, stimulating a voluntary and progressive improvement in their behaviour and increasing their <a href=\"/wiki/Motivation\" title=\"Motivation\">motivation</a> towards the achievement of academic objectives.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <b>Vivo Miles</b> is a system of extrinsic rewards based on the principles of the <a href=\"/wiki/Token_economy\" title=\"Token economy\">Token economy</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Positive_reinforcement#Positive_and_negative_reinforcement\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Positive reinforcement\">positive reinforcement</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> There has long been a debate about the use of extrinsic rewards and the effect that they may, or may not have on pupils' motivation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mechanism\">Mechanism</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Mechanism\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Vivo Class uses a simulated <a href=\"/wiki/Economic_system\" title=\"Economic system\">economic system</a> where the currency are electronic points called <b>Vivos</b> (pronounced Vee-vos). School teachers award their students Vivos for their achievements and positive actions according to the reward criteria set by their tutors and school management. Every school customises the rewards platform in line with their own goals based upon their academic initiatives, objectives and ethos. Teachers have access to an online platform where they can manage the number of points or Vivos awarded to every student.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Each pupil gets a private online profile where they can check how many points they have earned and know the actions they were rewarded for as well as the teacher or member of the school staff that awarded those points. Students can redeem their points in an online catalogue where they can choose from a range of products approved by the school management and partly selected by them in consensus.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Financial_Learning\">Financial Learning</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Financial Learning\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>One intention is that pupils are introduced to the concepts of economy and <a href=\"/wiki/Personal_finance\" title=\"Personal finance\">personal finance</a> in a context that emulates the socio-political system in which they are immersed which helps prepare them for real-life situations such as the planning and control of their own finances.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Students have a <a href=\"/wiki/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">currency</a> (Vivos points) and a plastic card similar to a <a href=\"/wiki/Bank_card\" title=\"Bank card\">bank account card</a>. Students decide how to manage the points they have earned. They can save their points and earn interest, accumulate them, or trade them for products. Students can only carry out transactions with the card within the Vivo platform. Students can also choose to donate their points to designated <a href=\"/wiki/Charities\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Charities\">charities</a> or to partner schools in <a href=\"/wiki/Developing_countries\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Developing countries\">developing countries</a>, all at the discretion of the school leadership team.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Parental_involvement\">Parental involvement</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Parental involvement\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Vivo Class has a platform for parents to monitor their child\u2019s activity online and be aware of their achievements and the way they have chosen to spend their points.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Financial_Value\">Financial Value</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Financial Value\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>For schools based in the United Kingdom, each Vivo point has an approximate value of 1 penny, in Great British Sterling. This can be seen in their online shop, where any voucher costs the same number of Vivo points as the voucher's worth in pence.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Awards_and_nominations\">Awards and nominations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Awards and nominations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In 2010 Vivo Miles was the winner at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bettawards.com/\">BETT Awards</a> in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bettshow.com/bett/website/PressDetails.aspx?PressId=pressRe132%20&amp;ExhId=&amp;refer=\">Leadership and Management Solutions category</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:1_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:1-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Vivo Miles was shortlisted for the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.educationinvestor.co.uk/awards.aspx/\">EducationInvestor Awards 2011</a>, for \"Use of Educational Technology\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-:1_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:1-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Behavior_management\" title=\"Behavior management\">Behavior management</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Classroom_management\" title=\"Classroom management\">Classroom management</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Every_Child_Matters\" title=\"Every Child Matters\">Every Child Matters</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Vivo_Class&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vivoclass.com/skills/about.html\">\"An online platform proven to realise student potential - VivoClass | Vivo Class\"</a>. <i>Vivo Class</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180615214738/https://www.vivoclass.com/skills/about.html\">Archived</a> from the original on 2018-06-15<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2018-06-15</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Vivo+Class&amp;rft.atitle=An+online+platform+proven+to+realise+student+potential+-+VivoClass+%7C+Vivo+Class&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vivoclass.com%2Fskills%2Fabout.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVivo+Class\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Slavin, R. (1999). <i>Educational Psychology: Theory and practice (6th ed.)</i>. Boston: Allyn and Bacon.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Educational+Psychology%3A+Theory+and+practice+%286th+ed.%29&amp;rft.place=Boston&amp;rft.pub=Allyn+and+Bacon&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.au=Slavin%2C+R.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVivo+Class\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Rawlings, Linda A. (2007). <i>Extrinsic rewards in schools: A look at practice in elementary school settings</i>. United States -- Utah: The University of Utah. p.&#160;83. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-549-30849-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-549-30849-2\">978-0-549-30849-2</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Extrinsic+rewards+in+schools%3A+A+look+at+practice+in+elementary+school+settings&amp;rft.place=United+States+--+Utah&amp;rft.pages=83&amp;rft.pub=The+University+of+Utah&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-549-30849-2&amp;rft.au=Rawlings%2C+Linda+A.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVivo+Class\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.calstatela.edu/faculty/jshindl/cm/ExtrinsicRewards.htm\">\"Some thoughts regarding the use of Extrinsic Rewards\"</a>. <i>web.calstatela.edu</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180706135601/https://web.calstatela.edu/faculty/jshindl/cm/ExtrinsicRewards.htm\">Archived</a> from the original on 2018-07-06<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2018-07-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=web.calstatela.edu&amp;rft.atitle=Some+thoughts+regarding+the+use+of+Extrinsic+Rewards&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.calstatela.edu%2Ffaculty%2Fjshindl%2Fcm%2FExtrinsicRewards.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVivo+Class\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:0-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_5-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_5-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vivoclass.com/docs/HowItWorks.pdf\">\"The Guide\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>vivoclass.com</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180706135601/htt